title: Grateful Dead Live at Veterans' Memorial Coliseum on 1984-04-24
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi CR5A > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab 2448 > R8Brain > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC 1644 tagged. Transfer by Andrew F. 11/2013
description:
Set 1

Bertha-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Candyman, Little Red Rooster, Bird Song, My Brother Esau, Ramble On Rose, It's All Over Now, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider-> Women Are Smarter, He's Gone-> Drums-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: U.S. Blues
